'''Ferḥat Mehenni''', d aselway n [[Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt n i Kvayeliyen|Umussu i Timanit n Tmurt n i Kvayliyen]] (M. A. K.), ilul-d deg [[5 Meɣres]] [[1951]] deg taddart n Illula, deg tama n temdinin n [[Buzegan]], [[Iaezzugen]], akk-d [[Akbu]]. 

Asmi i d-kemmel almad-ines deg Tesdawit n [[Lezzayer]] (tamaneɣt) yevda-d tikli-ines di ccna deg [[1973]] imi yewwi tarrazt tamezwarut n tafaska tatrart n ccna n Lezzayer. 
Kra n wukud sin akkin isbeggen-d iman-is d akken yella mgal unabad n iɣil n Lezzayer imi yevda-d avrid n tigwin ; ɣef igiten agi yekcem-d ɣer temufrikt 13 iverdan. 

Sakin (sin akkin) [[Tafsut Taverkant]], imi Tamselta n Lezzayer tenɣa yiwen weqcic amelsi yettusemman [[Masinisa Germah]], Ferhat Mhenni isbed ''Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt'' ; tuddsa ixeddmen akken a tessiwed ar timanit n tmurt n yekvayliyen. Llan wid i nnan d akken ɣef demma n wannecta i yettwanɣa mmi-s Amezian Mehenni deg [[2004]], di Tamanaɣt n Fṛansa, Paris. 

Amussu i Timanit n Tamurt (MAK), [[Agraw i Yedles d Tugdut]] (RCD), akk-d [[Tirni Iɣallen Inemlayen]] (FFS) d ikabaren isertiyen i lin (sann) azal deg [[Tamurt n el Kvayel|Tmurt n Izwawen]]. 

